(29903, 'darunavir ethanolate and cobicistat', 'N/A', 'moderate', 'Amlodipine, diltiazem, felodipine, nifedipine, verapamil ↑ calcium channel blockers Clinical monitoring is recommended for co-administration with calcium channel blockers metabolized by CYP3A.', 'DailyMed'),
