(32142, 'fosamprenavir calcium', 'N/A', 'moderate', 'Calcium channel blockers: Diltiazem, felodipine, nifedipine, nicardipine, nimodipine, verapamil, amlodipine, nisoldipine, isradipine ↑Calcium channel blockers Use with caution.', 'DailyMed'),
