(22226, 'finasteride and tadalafil', 'N/A', 'minor', 'Clinical pharmacology studies were conducted to assess the effect of tadalafil on the potentiation of the blood-pressure-lowering effects of selected antihypertensive medications (amlodipine, angiotensin II receptor blockers, bendrofluazide, enalapril, and metoprolol).', 'DailyMed'),
